112/04/23<br />英文會議討論主題<br /><br />The topic of this week; let’s discuss Taiwan’s scenic spots or Taiwan’s customs and culture, because we have lived in Taiwan for so many years and have also been to ordinary scenic spots. Of course, we have also learned about the customs and cultures of various places, but we  There must be members who have never been there or don't know, so please come and explain what you know and introduce each other. Thank you!<br /><br />The first topic ; introduce the scenic spots in Taiwan!<br />1: The first question introduces the National Palace Museum in Taipei!<br />2: The second question is to introduce the scenic areas of Sun Moon Lake!<br />3: The third question is to introduce the Alishan Forest Recreation Area!<br />4: The fourth question is to introduce Taroko National Park!<br />5: The fifth question is to introduce the Zhiben Hot Spring in Taitung!<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00:8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />SECT.2 <br />The second topic :is the introduction of Taiwanese customs and culture!<br />1: The first question, please explain the culture of Ching Ming Festival, such as eating moist cakes!(潤餅）<br />2: The second question is about aboriginal festivals, such as the Harvest Festival!<br />3: The third question is to discuss the current Buddhist culture in Taiwan!<br />4: The fourth question is about Mazu's Surroundings activities as far as you know!<br />5: The fifth question is to discuss the shock (收驚）culture of Xingtian Temple in Taipei!<p>Statistics: Posted